1. Raw Proxmox payload (from <code>/cluster/resources</code>)2. Pydantic model validation (<code>models.py</code>)3. NetBox payload (from mapper)4. netbox-sdk API call <pre><code>{
  "vmid": 100,
  "name": "web-server-01",
  "type": "qemu",
